<h2 id="others">Others</h2>
<p>Currently jekyll-paginate plugin doesn‚Äôt allow paging over groups of posts linked by a common tag or category. 
The more recent <a href="https://github.com/sverrirs/jekyll-paginate-v2">jekyll-paginate-v2</a> plugin can support the pagination for categories, tags and collections. See the pagination examples in the repository.<br /> <strong>This plugin is not supported by GitHub Pages. I haven‚Äôt tried it!</strong> üôÇ</p>
